snippet.title: Tails Noir: Rebel Rush (release trailer)
snippet.description:
Rebel Rush is a single-player speedrunning driving platformer where you sacrifice himbos for hideous carkour moves. 

Made by Soup with Friends, published by EggNut, 2024.

Available on Steam now!
